      "span_text": "Recent studies have suggested that SarMet SP is susceptible to the action of proteases that are up-regulated in the estrogen-dominated rat uterus [CITATION_1] , which may partially explain the reduction in response to SarMet SP in estrogen-dominated versus non-estrogen-dominated states."
